{"word":"G1330 - διέρχομαι - diérchomai - dee-er'-khom-ahee - Come","slug":"G1330","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diérchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-er'-khom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - dierchomai</b> - <i>dee-er'-khom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>; to <i>traverse</i> (literally): - come, depart, go (about, abroad, every where, over, through, throughout), pass (by, over, through, throughout), pierce through, travel, walk through."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565\">G565</a>"}]}